<h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
  <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> September 30, 2025</p>

  <p>We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This policy explains what data we collect, how we use it, and your rights regarding that information.</p>

  <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>When visitors fill out our contact form, we collect their <strong>name, email address, and phone number</strong>.</li>
    <li>When they use the <strong>Calendly widget</strong>, Calendly may collect scheduling data and contact details.</li>
    <li>We use <strong>Umami Analytics</strong> to understand how visitors interact with our website. Umami does <em>not</em> use cookies or collect personally identifiable information. It tracks anonymous data such as:
      <ul>
        <li>Pages visited</li>
        <li>Device type</li>
        <li>Referrer information</li>
      </ul>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>To respond to inquiries</li>
    <li>To schedule and manage lessons</li>
    <li>To improve our website and services</li>
  </ul>
  <p>We do <strong>not</strong> sell or share your personal data with third parties.</p>

  <h2>3. Third-Party Services</h2>
  <p>We use <a href="https://calendly.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Calendly</a> to manage lesson scheduling. Calendly may collect and store personal information according to its own privacy policy.</p>

  <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
  <p>We take reasonable steps to protect your information, including secure email and limited access to submitted data.</p>

  <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
  <p>You may request to:</p>
  <ul>
    <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
    <li>Correct or update your information</li>
    <li>Delete your data from our records</li>
  </ul>
  <p>To make a request, please use the contact form at <a href="studio.sarette.net/contact">studio.sarette.net/contact</a>.</p>
